<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">

<style media="screen">
  * {
    font-family: Calibri;
    font-size: 13pt;
  }
</style>

<div class="container">
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-5">Registration Confirmation</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <p>Hey <b><%= username %></b>,</p>
      <p>Thanks for registering! We are keen to see you apart of our community! But, before you jump in, you need to do 1 more thing for us.. you will need to confirm your Minecraft Account with our Services, read on to see how to do it!</p>

      <p>To complete your registration, join our Network (<code><%= serverip %></code>) and type the following command: <code>/link <%= token %></code><br>Once this is done, you should recieve a message saying that registration has been completed!</p>

      <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
        <p>This is a new system so there are bound to be issues. Please report them GitHub <a href="<%= githubissuetrackerlink %>">here</a>, talk to us on our Discord <a href="<%= discordlink %>">here</a> or contact our Support team at <a href="mailto:<%= contactemail %>"><%= contactemail %></a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
